<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url(https://asset.sipsmith.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/19183734/Cocktail-Ingredients_Greenery_credit-jacoblundiStock-httpswww.istockphoto.comgbphotobarman-preparing-basil-smash-cocktail-gm585054878-100244271.jpg);">
